Package: umit
Version: 0.9.4
Revision: 1
Description: Advanced Python-based GUI for nmap
DescUsage: Must be run as root user or with sudo.

Maintainer: Daniel Johnson <daniel@daniel-johnson.org>
License: GPL
Homepage: http://umit.sourceforge.net/

Source: http://download.insecure.org/nmap/dist/nmap-4.22SOC2.tar.bz2
Source-MD5: 678faf0402b838450071ae0cdffcf52a
SourceDirectory: nmap-4.22SOC2

Depends: python25, nmap | nmap-nox, pygtk2-gtk-py25, pysqlite2-py25

DocFiles: umit/COPYING umit/COPYING_HIGWIDGETS umit/README

CompileScript: <<
 cd umit; %p/bin/python2.5 setup.py build
<<
InstallScript: <<
 cd umit; %p/bin/python2.5 setup.py install --root %d
 /bin/rm %i/bin/uninstall_umit
 perl -pi -e 's,\Q%d\E,,g' %i/bin/umit %i/share/umit/config/umit.conf
<<
